ai-patthana23.26:0.2_0: under the influence of the Dhamma: the Protector of the Three Worlds
ai-patthana23.26:0.3_0: Seeing what is good, one is good.
ai-patthana23.26:1.1_0: Not seeing, you should give up a teaching, not skilled in seeing, and you should give up those conditions.
ai-patthana23.26:1.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
ai-patthana23.26:2.1_0: Not seeing, they should give up the unskillful qualities that should be given up by not seeing, by seeing, and with a reason.
ai-patthana23.26:3.1_0: One should not give up in order to indulging in not meetings with causes and reasons. This is the reason for developing.
